childAltar.hintText: 3 Spiritual Stones found in Hyrule...^$0Zora's Domain...^$1Gerudo's Fortress...^$2Kakariko Village...^$oYe who may become a Hero...&The path to the future is open...

adultAltar.hintText: An awakening voice from the Sacred&Realm will call those destined to be&Sages, who dwell in the five temples.^$8Kokiri Forest...^$3The Lost Woods...^$4Sacred Forest Meadow...^$5Kakariko Village...^$6Zora's Domain...^$7Goron City...^$lThe awakened ones will await&for the Hero to collect&6 Spiritual Stones and Medallions.^$bAnd the %revil one%w's key will&be hidden somewhere %rinside&its castle%w.^$kTogether with the Hero of Time,&the awakened ones will return&the light of peace to the world...

ganonText: I've learned this spell,&it's really neat,&I'll keep it later&for your treat!
ganonHintText: Ha ha ha... You'll never beat me&by reflecting my lightning bolts&and unleashing the arrows from %ra&high mountain%w!
sheikText: I overheard Ganondorf say that he&misplaced the %yLight Arrows%w in&%ra high mountain%w.
dampeText: Whoever reads this, please enter&%ran immense cavern%w. I will let&you have my stretching, shrinking&keepsake.^I'm waiting for you.&--Dampé
dampeHintLoc: Dodongos Cavern MQ Torch Puzzle Room Chest
gregText: By the way, if you're interested,&I saw the shiniest %gGreen Rupee%w&somewhere in%g Gerudo Valley%w.^It's said to have %rmysterious&powers%w...^But then, it could just be another&regular rupee.&Oh well.
sariaText: Did you feel the %gsurge of&magic%w recently? A mysterious&bird told me it came from %gHyrule&Field%w.^You should check that place out,&@!$C
